Ainda estou desenvolvendo esse bash script, então esse readme ainda vai ser melhor elaborado





run <file> — compile and run

run -c <file> — compile
run -e <file> — execute an alreary build executable or interpreter
run -i <file> — interprete intead of compile (if avaliable)

run --java <project_root_dir> — compile and run a java project
run -c --java <project_root_dir> — build the .jar  and .classes
run -e --java <project_root_dir> — run the .jar file
run -i --java <project_root_dir> — run the .classes files



